text: Sarah Witry (born 6 September 2002) is a Luxembourger footballer who plays as a defender for Dames Ligue 1 club SC Bettembourg and the Luxembourg women's national team. ==References== Category:2002 births Category:Living people Category:Women's association football defenders Category:Luxembourgian women's footballers Category:Luxembourg women's international footballers
